data.description: TERRIFIC single-family, ranch-style home in Longmont! Your future home offers 3 Bedrooms and 2 Bathrooms. The main level has a spacious Living Room with large windows bringing in natural light, eat-in Kitchen, and Laundry (appliances negotiable). Primary Bedroom has a private 3/4 bath. Fenced back yard with covered patio is perfect for entertaining around your favorite grill! Mature trees offer shade and privacy! 2-car attached garage and extended driveway. Call now to schedule your showing!
